---
// Premium Hero Section 
---
<section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 lg:pt-48 lg:pb-32 overflow-hidden flex items-center min-h-screen">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 h-full w-full bg-white bg-[radial-gradient(#e5e7eb_1px,transparent_1px)] [background-size:16px_16px] opacity-40"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -z-10 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-primary/5 rounded-full blur-3xl translate-x-1/3 -translate-y-1/4"></div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10 w-full">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-light border border-gray-200 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-8 shadow-sm">
                <span class="relative flex h-2.5 w-2.5">
                  <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-primary opacity-75"></span>
                  <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2.5 w-2.5 bg-primary"></span>
                </span>
                Gamith Kisal | Premium Digital Architect
            </div>
            
            <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-dark leading-[1.1] mb-6">
                Engineering <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-blue-400">World-Class</span> <br /> 
                Digital Products.
            </h1>
            
            <p class="text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-600 mb-10 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
                I transform complex business challenges into elite software solutions and premium brand identities. Built for scale, designed for excellence.
            </p>
            
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
                <a href="#portfolio" class="inline-flex justify-center items-center px-8 py-4 text-base font-bold text-white bg-primary hover:bg-blue-700 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgb(15,98,254,0.3)] hover:shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgb(15,98,254,0.5)] hover:-translate-y-1">
                    Explore My Work
                </a>
                <a href="#contact" class="inline-flex justify-center items-center px-8 py-4 text-base font-bold text-dark bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 hover:border-dark rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
                    Book a Consultation
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>